title: Supernatural - Season 3  Episodes 11-16
description:
[b]'SCARY JUST GOT SEXY!'[/b]

How true these words are!  This show follows the travels of the Winchester brothers, Dean and Sam, who search out the paranormal with a vengeance and help save many lives from vampires, werewolves, ghosts, you name it they've killed it!

[b]Jensen Ackles[/b] (from Dawson's Creek, Smallville and Dark Angel) is the older brother, Dean, who looks after his younger brother, Sam, played by [b]Jared Padalecki[/b] (from The Gilmore Girls) who has psychic powers from his encounter with a demon when he was a baby and his mother was killed.  The brothers' father, John, trained them from an early age to be hunters but Sam left to begin a normal life at college and met Jessica, who he fell in love with.  When John went missing Dean turned to Sam for help, then when Jess was killed by the yellow-eyed demon who had killed their mother, Mary, the brothers went back on the road to seek vengeance and help others who were desperate.


THERE WHERE ONLY 16 EPISODES MADE THIS SEASON.
